                "invention-title": [
                    "Novel preparation method of glufosinate-ammonium salt",
                    "一种新的草铵膦盐的制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of pesticides, and particularly discloses a novel preparation method of glufosinate-ammonium salt. The invention relates to a novel preparation method of glufosinate-ammonium salt, which comprises the following steps: adding low-concentration ammonia water into a pressure kettle, and introducing carbon dioxide to form an ammonium bicarbonate aqueous solution; adding 3-(methyl hydroxyl phosphonyl) propionaldehyde into the ammonium bicarbonate aqueous solution, and carrying out heat preservation reaction to obtain a reaction solution; introducing hydrogen cyanide gas into the reaction liquid, and carrying out heat preservation reaction to obtain 2-(methyl hydroxyl phosphonyl) ethyl-2-methylene imidazoline-4-ketone; the method comprises the following steps: adding 2-(methyl hydroxyl phosphonyl) ethyl-2-methylene imidazoline-4-ketone into a high-pressure kettle, introducing ammonia gas, and carrying out ammonolysis, so as to obtain glufosinate ammonium mother liquor; excessive ammonia gas in the glufosinate-ammonium mother liquor is discharged; distilling and dehydrating the glufosinate-ammonium mother liquor from which the excessive ammonia gas is removed, so as to obtain a concentrated material; and adding the concentrated material into an alcohol precipitation kettle, crystallizing and precipitating from an alcohol solution, and finally centrifuging and drying to obtain a glufosinate-ammonium solid product."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本申请涉及农药的技术领域，具体公开了一种新的草铵膦盐的制备方法。一种新的草铵膦盐的制备方法，包括以下步骤：向压力釜中加入低浓度氨水，通入二氧化碳，形成碳酸氢铵水溶液；向碳酸氢铵水溶液中加入3‑（甲基羟基膦酰基）丙醛，并保温反应，得到反应液；向反应液中通入氰化氢气体，保温反应得到2‑（甲基羟基膦酰基）乙基‑2‑亚甲基咪唑啉‑4‑酮；将2‑（甲基羟基膦酰基）乙基‑2‑亚甲基咪唑啉‑4‑酮加入到高压釜中，通入氨气，氨解，得到草铵膦母液；将草铵膦母液中的过量氨气排出；将排除过量氨气后的草铵膦母液进行蒸馏脱水，得到浓缩料；将浓缩料加入到醇析釜中，从醇溶液中结晶析出，最后离心、干燥，得到草铵膦固体产品。"
                }
